        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6895",
        "content": "\"By the deported snakes!\" he exclaimed, \"Jawn McCaskey and his lady have been fightin' for an hour and a quarter by the watch.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
