        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6895",
        "content": "'He knocked him over,' I replied, liking sometimes to use such idioms, with the double object of teaching and perplexing her.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
