        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6895",
        "content": "'Well,' said I, 'you have seen bones all around you, and the bones of your mother, and you can feel the bones in your fingers.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
