        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6895",
        "content": "This, for several minutes, she did not answer, sitting with her back half toward me, cracking almonds, continually striking one step with the ball of her outstretched foot.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
