        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6895",
        "content": "She turned and drank some wine from the great gold Jarvan goblet which I had brought from the temple of Boro Budor, her head quite covered in by it. Then, the little hairs at her lip corners still wet, says she:",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
