        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6895",
        "content": "You understand, Clodagh, that originally the earth produced men by a long process, beginning with a very low type of creature, and continually developing it, until at last a man stood up.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
